The downloadable documents contain 9 worksheets, including information about the template, notes related to revisions of the template, resource provider information, the data, a field list (data mapping view) and a worksheet with vocabularies for use in populating the spreadsheet (data valid terms). Fields in the data table include Well Name, API Number, Ended Drilling Date, Well Type, Bottom Logged Interval,and Log Notes. </dct:description>         <dcat:keyword>north america</dcat:keyword>
